headline: 1 Healthcare Stock to Consider Right Now and 2 We Find Risky
summary: From novel pharmaceuticals to telemedicine, most healthcare companies are on a mission to drive better patient outcomes. Players catalyzing medical advancements have benefited from elevated demand, and their momentum is only rising as the industry has posted a 21.1% gain over the past six months, beating the S&P 500 by 10.6 percentage points.
